The '''Superlaser Simulator''' was a room in [[Theta Sector]] of the first [[DS-1 Orbital Battle Station/Legends|Death Star]] where [[Imperial gunner/Legends|gunners]] assigned to [[Superlaser Fire Control]] could practice prior to the completed installation of the Death Star Superlaser.<ref name="Death Star">[[Death Star (novel)|''Death Star'']]</ref>

